body:
Right now (patch 5.19) Rengar&#039;s passive has only 4 effects with max of 20 trophies but Riot i believe there should be 30 trophies with 1 new effect.
Something like.....bonus vision during Thrill of the hunt. But in late game it makes the rengar players feel more achievable space. (in my opinion)
But yes, i believe most of us would want another effect and more tooth stacks.{{champion:107}}
